Authors of perlmod_bldr

Created by Lee Thompson

See also the files THANKS and ChangeLog.

Note - this package contains a bundle of numerous perl modules written and
maintained by numerous PERL developers and hosted on CPAN.org.  The source
release of all these upstream works is contained in their intirety.


Lee Thompson, while installing perl 5.10.0, caught the addition of CPANPLUS
into the main perl package which inspired the creation of a "from source"
perl module bundling and release mechanism

